casebody.data:
No. 10-8395. Raymond L. Semler, Petitioner v. Crow Wing County Social Services, et al. 562 U.S. 1283, 131 S. Ct. 1687,

179 L. Ed. 2d 611,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 2147. March 21, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Minnesota dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
